<p>It's worth noting that not all Lindor Truffles varieties are created equal when it comes to gluten content. Some flavors may contain ingredients that are more likely to include gluten, such as cookie pieces or other additives. Below is a comparison table of different Lindor Truffles varieties and their gluten status:</p>

